(165, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.org/news/2012/12/elvin/'' title=''It’s the most wonderful time of the year: a new WordPress release is available and chock-full of goodies to delight bloggers and developers alike. We’re calling this one “Elvin” in honor of drummer Elvin Jones, who played with John Coltrane in addition to many others. If you’ve been around WordPress a while, the most dramatic [&hellip;]''>WordPress 3.5 “Elvin”</a> <span class="rss-date">11 de dezembro de 2012</span><div class=''rssSummary''>It’s the most wonderful time of the year: a new WordPress release is available and chock-full of goodies to delight bloggers and developers alike. We’re calling this one “Elvin” in honor of drummer Elvin Jones, who played with John Coltrane in addition to many others. If you’ve been around WordPress a while, the most dramatic [&hellip;]</div></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wordpress.org/news/2012/12/wordpress-3-5-release-candidate-3/'' title=''The third release candidate for WordPress 3.5 is now available. We’ve made a number of changes over the last week since RC2 that we can’t wait to get into your hands. Hope you’re ready to do some testing! Final UI improvements for the new media manager, based on lots of great feedback. Show more information about [&hellip;]''>WordPress 3.5 Release Candidate 3</a> <span class="rss-date">4 de dezembro de 2012</span><div class=''rssSummary''>The third release candidate for WordPress 3.5 is now available. We’ve made a number of changes over the last week since RC2 that we can’t wait to get into your hands. Hope you’re ready to do some testing! Final UI improvements for the new media manager, based on lots of great feedback. Show more information about [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
